 Derive ~ ax-9 from ~ ax-i9 , the modified version for intuitionistic logic.  Although ~ ax-9 does hold intuistionistically, in intuitionistic logic it is weaker than ~ ax-i9 .  (Contributed by NM, 3-Feb-2015.)
